title: American Horror Story : Coven-  Final Scene

comment: This is probably the happiest ending of any AHS so far.
Sometimes the only thing that keeps me going is knowing that somewhere in the AHS universe Cordelia is still alive and living her dream
kyle had such hopes and dreams for himself now he just wants to be a butler
Don't know if y'all noticed the face Cordelia makes when the girl asks who's the supreme. Like she's already trying to locate her successor.
